headline: STRADVISION Wins 2025 AI Breakthrough Award for SVNet
summary: STRADVISION, a trailblazer in AI-driven perception technology for the automotive industry, today announced that its flagship software product, SVNet, was honored as a winner in the 2025 AI Breakthrough Awards. This distinguished accolade places STRADVISION alongside global innovators such as NVIDIA, Meta, Microsoft, Qualcomm, and UiPath, affirming its position as a top-tier innovator in artificial intelligence.

headline: AI Chips Update - AI App Transforms Secondhand Market With Real-Time Valuations
summary: WhatsitAI, an AI-powered mobile app designed to identify and value secondhand items, has achieved over 50,000 downloads shortly after its launch. The app allows users to take a photo of an item to instantly see its identification, estimated value, and where similar items can be purchased online, using data aggregated from major resale marketplaces.
